description: Introducing the all-new 2025 Nissan Pathfinder Platinum, a premium 4D Sport Utility that combines comfort, capability, and cutting-edge technology. This SUV is designed for those who crave adventure without sacrificing luxury.Finished in a stunning White Pearl exterior, the Pathfinder exudes elegance and a bold presence on the road. Its sleek lines and modern design are complemented by the advanced engineering under the hood.Under the hood, you'll find a robust 3.5L V6 DOHC engine paired with a 9-speed automatic transmission. The drivetrain is a 4WD configuration, ensuring excellent handling and performance in various driving conditions. Enjoy efficient power delivery with a respectable fuel economy of 20 mpg in the city and 25 mpg on the highway.Step inside to a spacious interior featuring a luscious Chestnut color palette. The Platinum trim level means you'll enjoy premium materials and finishes throughout the cabin.Key features include:- Luxurious Leather Seating: Provides ultimate comfort and sophistication.- Advanced Safety Systems: Equipped with Nissan's latest safety technologies to keep you and your passengers secure.- Intuitive Infotainment System: Enjoy a suite of connectivity options and an easy-to-use interface.- Panoramic Sunroof: Adds an airy feel to the cabin and lets you enjoy the view above.With only 5 miles on the odometer, this Pathfinder is practically fresh off the production line, ready to embark on its journeys with you.Whether you're commuting through the city or exploring the great outdoors, the 2025 Nissan Pathfinder Platinum offers the versatility and luxury you need. Contact Alpine Nissan today at 720-880-1327  and discover what makes this SUV the perfect choice for your next adventure.

description:
Clean CARFAX.

Powerful and efficient, our 2018 Chevrolet Equinox LS SUV is sensational in Nightfall Gray Metallic! Powered by a TurboCharged 1.5 Liter 4 Cylinder that offers 170hp while connected to a responsive 6 Speed Automatic transmission for easy passing. This capable Front Wheel Drive SUV is going to please you with its confident demeanor as it handles beautifully, while also rewarding your wallet with near 32mpg on the highway. Our Equinox LS strikes a perfect balance of sporty sophistication with its sweeping silhouette. Halogen headlamps, outside heated power-adjustable mirrors, solar-absorbing glass, and great-looking wheels emphasize the smart styling.

The LS interior boasts ample cargo space, heated cloth seats, and lots of head/leg room to make everyone happy. Chevrolet MyLink audio system with a color touchscreen, a USB port, available WiFi, smartphone compatibility, power windows/locks, push-button start, and keyless open add to the comfort and convenience.

Safety is paramount with Chevrolet, evidenced by an airbag system, LED daytime running lamps, a rear vision camera, StabiliTrak, Teen Driver Technology, and other safety innovations. Chevrolet is committed to automotive excellence and has a sterling reputation for reliability, security, and performance that will add to your peace of mind each time you get behind the wheel of your Equinox.

When you do business with Todd Wenzel, we want you to have a premium experience; that is why we offer the Todd Wenzel Platinum Rewards Program to our customers. With the Todd Wenzel Platinum Rewards Program, we reward you for doing business with us. You can expect to receive VIP service like free multi-point inspections and on-demand courtesy vehicles at no charge. Purchase a GM Certified Pre-Owned vehicle and you'll also earn My GM Rewards points for purchases of GM products and services to redeem for discounts on future purchases and services. It's that simple.

description:
Introducing the 2018 Ford Focus Titanium - the ultimate combination of style, performance, and technology. This sleek and modern sedan is designed to turn heads, with its bold grille and striking lines. But it's not just about looks - under the hood, you'll find a powerful 2.0L Ti-VCT engine, delivering 160 horsepower and impressive fuel efficiency.

Step inside and experience the luxurious interior, complete with leather-trimmed seats and advanced features such as the SYNC 3 infotainment system, which allows you to stay connected and entertained on the go. And with the Titanium trim level, you'll also enjoy added convenience and safety features like a navigation system, rearview camera, and blind spot monitoring.

But the 2018 Ford Focus Titanium isn't just about style and technology - it also offers a smooth and responsive ride, thanks to its independent suspension and electric power-assisted steering. Plus, with its advanced safety features, including a full suite of airbags, you can feel confident and secure behind the wheel.

Don't miss your chance to own the 2018 Ford Focus Titanium - a car that offers both sophistication and performance. Visit us today to take a test drive and see for yourself why this sedan is a top choice for drivers who demand the best.

This 2018 Jeep Cherokee Latitude Plus is a versatile and well-equipped SUV that's ready to take on your daily adventures. Featuring a 2.4L I4 engine and 9-speed automatic transmission, this Cherokee delivers an impressive blend of power and efficiency, with EPA-estimated ratings of 21 MPG in the city and 30 MPG on the highway.

Key features include:
Comfort/Convenience Group
Cold Weather Group
Compact Spare Tire

This Jeep comes equipped with a host of premium amenities to enhance your driving experience, including:
Dual-zone automatic climate control
Heated front seats and steering wheel
Power liftgate
Remote start
Rearview camera
Blind spot monitoring
And much more

The sleek gray exterior and spacious interior make this Latitude Plus model a standout in its class. With seating for up to five and generous cargo space, it's the perfect companion for your family, your hobbies, or your next road trip.

Whether you're looking for a capable and comfortable SUV for your daily commute or a versatile vehicle for your active lifestyle, this 2018 Jeep Cherokee Latitude Plus is an excellent choice. With its impressive features, efficient powertrain, and stylish design, it's sure to exceed your expectations.

We invite you to come in and experience this exceptional Jeep for yourself. Our knowledgeable sales team is here to answer any questions you may have and help you discover why this Cherokee is the perfect fit for your needs. Don't miss out on this opportunity to own a well-equipped and well-maintained Jeep at an exceptional value.

We look forward to the opportunity to earn your business and help you find the perfect vehicle. Stop by our showroom today and let's get you behind the wheel of this impressive 2018 Jeep Cherokee Latitude Plus.
